;
; Used by the routine at #R$828C.
;
; .
;
; Called from #R$828C. Copies the fixed (non-paged) tile data at $82BE into the
; bottom-screen area starting $5000 (row 16), in a 4x2x8 nested-loop pattern (8
; columns x 2 rows x 4-byte strips). Same shared for every room - see the Draw
; pipeline section in docs/Room-Format.md.
@label=DrawBottomDoor
