; cleanly divide the observed #R$8901-$8963 span into fixed 16-byte chunks
; though (name lengths vary 7-8 chars) - the $8210*16 stride from the code
; doesn't match what's visible here byte-for-byte, so exact row layout is
; unconfirmed; needs live tracing (watch $8210 and this region during an actual
; high-score entry). Was previously fragmented into ~13 spurious t/b blocks by
; the same sna2skool text-detection heuristic fixed for #R$9D00/#R$6C00.
