; Writes the selected character ($8202) into the current table row at $8900 +
; $8210*16 + $0A + cursor column ($8201), then plays a beep (#R$856E). Part of
; the same cluster as #R$850E/#R$8982 (digit-roll + sort) - together they
; implement entering initials for a new high score.
@label=HiScoreStoreChar
