; Collectible tile-ID tables (keys/food/bombs/ammo/hostages/uniform)
;
; .
;
; .
;
; Flat byte arrays of raw room-tile indices ($8202-space, 0-127), one byte per
; collectible instance, not sorted. No count/header stored in the data - the
; scanning code (#R$912C/#R$926E/#R$92A0/#R$9300/#R$9328 for the first 4,
; #R$A2F6/#R$A328/#R$7B1E for ammo/uniform) has the entry count hardcoded.
; 2-byte gaps between some tables (e.g. $9D1E-$9D1F, $9D22-$9D23) are
; unaccounted for - not yet part of any known table.
